::Feline::

She smiled at the compliment. She looked up at K-9, "well, at least 
he's in a good mood." She smiled and went over to her work bench,  
She picked up some wires and a few pieces of plate metal and started 
repairs.  She worked on his head and neck first. "Now hold still.  I 
don't to have to sedate you, but I will if I have to."
as she soldered a few wires together.
